    <slide title="Storyboard Demo" layout="normal">
        <p>This slideshow presents a run-through of a small agile
            project, using PivotalTracker.</p>
        <p>It is not the only way to handle this - it is
            intended to illustrate one way that an agile project
            might be managed.</p>
        <p>We will be doing this in lab today - wait until then
            to try it!</p>
    </slide>

